  to you ,  |strong="413" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.14" \w* \w  ‘ The donkeys  |strong="860" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.16" \w* \w  -  |strong="834" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.17" \w* \w  you seek  |strong="1980" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.18" \w* \w  . . .  |strong="1245" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.19" \w* \w  have been found ,  |strong="4672" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.15" \w* \w  and now  |strong="2009" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.20" \w* \w  your father  |strong="1" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.22" \w* \w  -  |strong="853" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.23" \w* \w  has stopped  |strong="5203" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.21" \w* \w  worrying about  |strong="1697" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.24" \w* \w  the donkeys  |strong="860" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.25" \w* \w  and started worrying  |strong="1672" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.26" \w* \w  about you ,  |srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.27" \w* \w  asking ,  |strong="559" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.28" \w* \w  “ What  |strong="4100" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.29" \w* \w  should I do  |strong="6213" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.30" \w* \w  about my son ?”’  |strong="1121" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.2.31" \w* \v 3 \w  Then you will go  |strong="2498" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.1" \w* \w  on  |strong="1973" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.3" \w* \w  from there  |strong="8033" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.2" \w* \w  until you come  |strong="935" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.4" \w* \w  to  |strong="5704" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.5" \w* \w  the Oak  |strong="436" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.6" \w* \f + \fr 10.3 \ft Or "Terebinth" or "Great Tree" \f* \w  of Tabor .  |strong="8396" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.7" \w* \w  Three  |strong="7969" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.10" \w* \w  men  |strong="582" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.11" \w* \w  going up  |strong="5927" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.12" \w* \w  to  |strong="413" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.13" \w* \w  God  |strong="430" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.14" \w* \w  vvv  |strong="1008" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.15" \w* \w  at Bethel  |strong="1008" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.16" \w* \w  will meet you  |strong="4672" srcloc="WLC:1SA.10.3.8" \w* \w  there ,  |strong="8033" srcloc="WLC:1SA.